<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="js" lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta content="width=device-width" name="viewport">
  <title>Add claim: Permanent Impairment | MyService</title>
  <link href="docs/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body class="uikit-body uikit-grid uikit-refactor">
  <noscript>
    <p role="alert">This website needs JavaScript to work properly.</p>
  </noscript>
  <nav class="uikit-skip-link">
    <a class="uikit-skip-link__link" href="#main-content">Skip to main content</a>
  </nav>
  <% include ../../../global/partials/header-topbar.ejs %>
    <% include ../../../global/partials/header-claims.ejs %>
      <% include ../partials/help-button.ejs %>
        <main>
          <div id="main-content" class="section-feature border-bottom--mild margin-above--none margin-below--none padding-below">
            <div class="container margin-above--none">
              <h1 class="margin-above--none">
                <span class="heading">Getting started</span>
              </h1>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-offset-2 col-md-8">

                <h2 class="margin-above--large">When determining your level of Permanent Impairment compensation, we look at the affect your conditions have
                  on your lifestyle.</h2>
                <h2>And no one knows how you've been affected better than you.
                </h2>

                <p class="margin-below">The Lifestyle Questionnaire is your opportunity to
                  <b>tell us how your conditions are affecting your life</b>. Your story will contribute to the decision on
                  your level of impairment and may result in a greater rate of compensation.</p>
                <p>Alternatively, we can decide how your lifestyle has been affected without hearing from you.</p>

                <div class="margin-below--extra">
                  <div class="ss-align--center">
                    <a id="comparison-button" class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary accordion accordion--button">Select an option to get started
                      <span class="accordion__trigger accordion__trigger--closed accordion__trigger--white"></span>
                    </a>
                  </div>
                  <div id="comparison-table" class="transition-content margin-above--large">

                    <div class="form-group">
                      <div class="mys-radio-group mys-radio-group--cols-2">
                        <label class="mys-radio">
                          <input id="lsq-pathway-tellstory" class="mys-radio__control" type="radio" name="home" value="no">
                          <span class="mys-radio__box mys-radio__box--large">
                            <img class="mys-radio__icon" src="../../../../docs/images/ico-message.svg">
                            <span>Complete a
                              <br>Lifestyle Questionnaire</span>
                          </span>
                        </label>
                        <label class="mys-radio">
                          <input id="lsq-pathway-dvadoit" class="mys-radio__control" type="radio" name="home" value="yes-a-little">
                          <span class="mys-radio__box mys-radio__box--large">
                            <img class="mys-radio__icon" src="../../../../docs/images/ico-folder.svg">
                            <span>Have DVA make a decision based on my medical reports.</span>
                          </span>
                        </label>
                      </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--info margin-below--large" style="display:none;" id="lsq-pathway-tellstory--info">
                      <p>Answer based on your worst day. Take into consideration all your accepted conditions. We have sent
                        you an email with the accepted conditions being assessed in this claim.
                      </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="pagination">
                      <button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary" onclick="window.location.href = '/auth?user=LSQuser'">Back to Claims page</button>
                      <div class="floated">
                        <button class="uikit-btn btnNext" id="btnNext">Save and next</button>
                      </div>
                    </div>

                  </div>
                </div>


              </div>
            </div>

            <% include ../partials/cancel-modal.ejs %>
          </div>

        </main>

        <% include ../../../global/partials/footer.ejs %>
          <% include ../partials/panel-help.ejs %>

            <script>

              // $('#comparison-table').hide();
              $("#comparison-button").click(function () {
                $("#comparison-table").toggleClass("transition-content--open");
                $(this).find('.accordion__trigger').toggleClass('accordion__trigger--closed');
              });


              $(".toggle-arrow ").click(function () {
                $(".simple-accordion ").toggleClass('simple-accordion--open simple-accordion--closed');
              });

              $(Document).ready(function () {
                $("#btnNext").click(function () { window.location.href = "/pi-lsq-claim1" });

                // Dynamic content for LSQ pathway
                $("#lsq-pathway-tellstory").click(function () {
                  $("#lsq-pathway-tellstory--info").show();
                });
                $("#lsq-pathway-dvadoit").click(function () {
                  $("#lsq-pathway-tellstory--info").hide();
                  $("#btnNext").click(function () { window.location.href = "/pi-lsq-claim6b" });
                });
              });
            </script>

</body>

</html>